    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Attention DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This car is a true survivor with a lot of stories to tell and is looking for a dedicated owner to bring it back to its former glory. While it shows significant wear and will require some mechanical TLC, it offers a fantastic foundation for a custom build or a rewarding restoration project. Grab this opportunity to own a vehicle with real soul and potential!",
